    <div class="comment-content">
    
    <p>Right now our current strategy centers mostly on Email marketing. We also make use of Affiliates which help promote our courses to their users.<br />
We&#8217;re not too fancy right now. For example we haven&#8217;t explored paid ads though some of our affiliates do paid ads.</p>
